tattoo ideas

    • https://xkcd.com/1428/

    • shorthand for "Be liberal in what you accept, and conservative in what you send"
    • Requirements for Internet Hosts - Robustness Principle

  • Astra mortemque praestare gradatim
    • The Utopian Hive motto
    • or, step-by-step to surpass both death and the stars
